## List of 50+ Hospitals

Healthcare is an important part of human life. As the saying goes, “Health is Wealth”.
Hospitals are the primary source of healthcare to people all over the world, therefore finding the right hospitals that offer the right health services to prospective patients is very important in finding the right health care for people. 
The aim of this project is to help people find the right hospital that can satisfy their medical needs effectively.
To do this, Below is a list of hospitals to help clients in making their choice of hospitals. 
This list will help to determine the best hospitals equipped to provide medical services for you .
They Include:
   
